				["CU"] = "His ears perk attentively to every conversation around him. He certainly is quite the curious lad. Or, a nosy kit?\n\nLooks more excited than usual. Did he meet a new friend?\n\nShopping for a source of silicon. His pet Hiekka is curiously sniffling away for trails of treasure as he maintained a kempt posture.",
