				["TE"] = 1,
				["T1"] = {
					["TX"] = "{h1:c}{col:ae3428}42acb751ebbeea75d973534401d470ef{/col}{/h1}\n{h2:c}{col:901d1e}Try not to think about it.{/col}{/h2}\n{img:Interface\\Challenges\\challenges-copper:256:256}\n\n{h2:c}{col:ae3428}Synopsis{/col}{/h2}\n\n{p:c}{col:ffffff}Who is this fellow...? He appears to be a bit more than half the size of a regular Vulpera. A bit small for someone with a presentiment as his. He does not seem to be much one for conversation, it seems, but his ears can be seen trickling about, as if every trace of sound was at his attention at all times. The shadow-like appearance about him gives question as to whether his manifestation is a ploy for tricks, or a side effect of his current circumstance. A hybrid of heavy plated armor and voldunai attire, with a logo that seemingly takes resemblance to a local caravan group, perhaps? Perhaps he is a source and manifestation of all hatred, perhaps an entity born by the process of an innocent mortal being having their darkness sucked out of them for the sole purposes of being researched on, due to the discovery of a powerful light beaming within him that was otherwise tainted and suppressed by the darkness? Or... perhaps he is just any regular being, and his entire appearance is a façade. Who can say, really?{/col}{/p}",
